                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17851214-25-off136 t17851214-25-cd137"></join> last, one leather pocket-book, value 3 s. 6 d. four other leather pocket-books, value 3 s. one New Testament, value 1 s. 6 d. one Spelling Dictionary, value 2 s. one Compleat Letter-writer, value 1 s. 6 d. one Hervey's Meditations, value 2 s. one Tragedy of Zara, value 1 s. 6 d.
